CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 12, 1953, pg. 2 reads: "Dreams Come True - Santa made a premature visit to the home of Mary London Little last week, and in process of doing so, made two of her dreams come true. Through the cooperation of Mrs. Eunice W. Cook, left, Mary was given a console television set and the wheelchair in which she is seated.  -Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Eunice Cook presenting television set and wheelchair to Mary London Little
